# Engineering Workbench product-glue (NOT a component file — see VENDORING.md).
#
# The component's own .gitignore says `evals/results/`, relying on the four
# scored summaries being ALREADY TRACKED in its home repo (gitignore never
# applies to tracked files). In this fresh product repo nothing is pre-tracked,
# so that directory rule would silently drop the committed eval artifacts the
# honest-eval chip reads. This deeper file takes precedence for this subtree
# and re-selects exactly the four files upstream tracks.
!results
results/*
!results/summary.json
!results/model_frontier.json
!results/adversarial.txt
!results/holdout
results/holdout/*
!results/holdout/summary_holdout.json
